    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the strength of the direct bench-test validation (N=11, two laboratories) and the conservative acceptance bounds applied to all QoIs. The FEA ensemble demonstrates sufficient credibility for the intended regulatory submission decision. Evidence from bench testing and material characterization is documented in the validation result records; the overall package is accepted at Medium assurance level.",
